      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple though. \"reaching out\" just makes it worse because they'll just use that against me too. everyone's just waiting for me to mess up so they can laugh more. i feel like i'm just existing in this cycle of being hated and there's no actual light at the end of it. it just feels like a dead end.",
